<br>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <svg class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="160">
      <image xlink:href="<%= image_path('admin.png') %>" width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/>
    </svg>
    <h2 class="fw-normal">Admin</h2>
    <p>Register Suppliers and Hospitals and Manage Overall System</p>
    <p><%= link_to 'Login &raquo;'.html_safe, addsuppliers_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary', id: 'loginId1' %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <svg class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="160">
      <image xlink:href="<%= image_path('supplier.jpg') %>" width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/>
    </svg>
    <h2 class="fw-normal">Suppliers</h2>
    <p>Collect Blood Units from Donors & ship it to the Authorized Hospitals</p>
    <p><%= link_to 'Login &raquo;'.html_safe, adddonors_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary', id: 'loginId2' %></p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-lg-4">
    <svg class="bd-placeholder-img rounded-circle" width="140" height="160">
      <image xlink:href="<%= image_path('hospital.png') %>" width="100%" height="100%" fill="#777"/>
    </svg>
    <h2 class="fw-normal">Hospitals</h2>
    <p>Collect Blood Samples from the Authorized Suppliers and use it in need for Patients</p>
    <p><%= link_to 'Login &raquo;'.html_safe, addpatients_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary', id: 'loginId3' %></p>
  </div>
  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">
        Hey!! Wanna Donate Blood?
        <%= link_to 'Explore Suppliers to Donate Blood & be a superhero &raquo;&raquo;&raquo;'.html_safe, suppliers_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary' %>
      </h2>
      <p class="lead">Do you feel you don't have much to offer? You have the most precious resource of all: the ability to save a life by donating blood! Help share this invaluable gift with someone in need</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
      <img class="d-block" width="400" height="350" src="<%= image_path('c3.jpg') %>">
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-7">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">Easily Track your Donated Blood</h2><br>
      <%= link_to 'Track your Blood Here &raquo;&raquo;&raquo; &raquo;&raquo;&raquo;'.html_safe, trackblood_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary' %>
      <p class="lead">We ensure you that your donated Blood will give hope to those in need & we respect your Contribution</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <img class="d-block w-40" width="400" height="300" src="<%= image_path('c2.jpg') %>">
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">

  <div class="row featurette">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading fw-normal lh-1">
        Oh yeah, it's that good.
        <%= link_to 'Check All Blood Samples Here &raquo;&raquo;&raquo;'.html_safe, bloodunits_path, class: 'btn btn-secondary' %>
      </h2>
      <p class="lead">The blood you donate gives someone another chance at life. One day that someone may be a close relative, a friend, a loved oneâ€”or even you</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
      <img class="d-block" width="400" height="350" src="<%= image_path('v1.jpg') %>">
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="featurette-divider">
</div>
